cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.HC, cs.NE 

The paper uses deep learning models to extract new knowledge from retinal fundus images and predict cardiovascular risk factors. This involves image analysis and machine learning, which are core topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves the use of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE) to train the deep learning models. Additionally, the paper discusses the potential clinical applications of the technology, which could involve human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
